                "name": "Strum the Swirling Winds",
                "img": "https:\/\/static.wikia.nocookie.net\/gensin-impact\/images\/8\/85\/Talent_Strum_the_Swirling_Winds.png",
                "text": "Mora expended when ascending Bows and Catalysts is decreased by 50%."
